iking in summer. Pack layers, waterproof gear, and be prepared for rapidly changing weather.',\n   255→      tags: JSON.stringify(['travel', 'hiking', 'europe']),\n   256→    },\n   257→    {\n   258→      title: 'Espresso Brewing Techniques',\n   259→      body: 'Perfect espresso requires freshly roasted beans, proper grind size, correct dose (18-20g), consistent tamping pressure, water temperature around 200°F, and 25-30 second extraction time. The result should be a balanced shot with a rich crema layer. Adjust grind size to control flow rate.',\n   260→      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'coffee', 'techniques']),\n   261→    },\n   262→    {\n   263→      title: 'Version Control with Git',\n   264→      body: 'Git is the most widely used version control system. Key commands include init, clone, add, commit, push, pull, branch, merge, and rebase. Use feature branches for development, pull requests for code review, and tags for releases. Write meaningful commit messages that explain why changes were made.',\n   265→      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'git', 'tools']),\n   266→    },\n   267→    {\n   268→      title: 'The Science of Sleep',\n   269→      body: 'Quality sleep is essential for health. Adults need 7-9 hours nightly. Sleep cycles through stages including light sleep, deep sleep, and REM. Improve sleep hygiene by maintaining consistent schedules, limiting screen time before bed, keeping rooms cool and dark, and avoiding caffeine after noon.',\n   270→      tags: JSON.stringify(['health', 'science', 'sleep']),\n   271→    },\n   272→    {\n   273→      title: 'Watercolor Painting Basics',\n   274→      body: 'Watercolor painting uses water-soluble pigments on paper. Start with basic techniques: wet-on-wet for soft blends, wet-on-dry for sharp edges, and dry brush for texture. Use quality paper (140lb cold press), a limited palette of primary colors, and practice controlling water ratios.',\n   275→      tags: JSON.stringify(['art', 'painting',